exotic /ɪɡˈzɒtɪk/

1. ADJ Something that is exotic is unusual and interesting, usually because it comes from or is related to a distant country. (常因来自遥远的他国而显得) 奇异的 

例： ...brilliantly coloured, exotic flowers. …色彩绚丽的奇异花卉。 

2. exotically ADV 奇异地 

例： ...exotically beautiful scenery. …奇异美景。

